#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:2 5d359b39a7574ebcb66275640eb50afe
msgid "NB-IoT2 Unit"
msgstr "NB-IoT2 Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:8 8e4143859042435fa1bcece6a9a441b9
msgid ""
"The ``NB-IOT2 Unit`` is a wireless communication module suitable for "
"global Cat-NB frequency bands. It features an integrated SIM7028 "
"communication module, utilizing serial communication (controlled via AT "
"commands)."
msgstr ""
"``NB-IOT2 Unit`` 是一款适用于全球 Cat-NB 频段的无线通信模块。它集成了 SIM7028 通信模块，并采用串口通信（通过 "
"AT commands 进行控制）。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:10 b9d21ef16a844178883e66a49fc968ce
msgid "Support the following products:"
msgstr "支持以下产品："

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:12 0d55c2ffa7c841dea7b5b3d0a94385d8
msgid "|NB-IOT2Unit|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/refs/unit.nbiot2.ref 1643d6ea83f947858a4e79849c74ea46
msgid "NB-IOT2Unit"
msgstr "NB-IOT2Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:16 c377e51ed0fa40ae84ca773847f1b50f
msgid ""
"Please ensure that the device supports the NB-IoT frequency bands in your"
" area before use."
msgstr "使用前请确保设备支持您所在地区的 NB-IoT 频段。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:20 f640e42d211144f1a2657632456e5452
msgid ""
"Please ensure that the firmware version of SIM7028 is greater than or "
"equal to **2110B07SIM7028**."
msgstr "请确保 SIM7028 的固件版本大于或等于 **2110B07SIM7028**。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot2.rst:22 9193633771ad47689fe6f2dd88ca4f33
